__DESCRIPTION__

In this video I am showing how easy it is to contribute a little bit to a Perl module on CPAN.
Specifically to the MIME::Lite module which has its version control repository on Github.

The related blog post can be found [here](http://perlmaven.com/contributing-to-a-perl-module-on-cpan-using-vim-and-github)

To see all the [Perl tutorials](http://perlmaven.com/perl-tutorial)

